## Installation

1. Clone the repository:  
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/Enhanced-ANPR.git
cd Enhanced-ANPR


2.Create and activate a virtual environment:

  python -m venv venv
  .\venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1

3.Install dependencies:
  pip install -r requirements.txt


How to Run 
Using a Video File

Place your video in test_videos/

In src/main.py, set:

VIDEO_SOURCE = "test_videos/car_video.mp4"


Run:

python src/main.py

Using a Webcam

In src/main.py, set:

VIDEO_SOURCE = 0


Run:

python src/main.py